'''H Mart'''（{{lang|ko|H 마트}}），又称'''韓亞龍'''（{{lang|ko|한아름}}），是由韩亚龙集团经营的美国连锁超级市场，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hmart.com/images/images_new/footer_logo.png|title=footer_logo.png|publisher=H Mart|accessdate=2011-06-26|archive-date=2012-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120727223500/http://hmart.com/images/images_new/footer_logo.png|dead-url=yes}}</ref>总部设于美国[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[博根縣|博根縣]]{{link-en|林德赫斯特 (新泽西)|Lyndhurst, New Jersey|林德赫斯特乡}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hmart.com/|title=韓亞龍购物网站|accessdate=2011-06-26|archive-date=2011-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808225211/http://www.hmart.com/|dead-url=yes}} "ADDRESS : 300 Chubb Ave. Lyndhurst, NJ 07071"</ref>超市遍布美国、加拿大和英國，专售亚洲食品。<ref>{{cite news|first=Christina|last=Pazzanese|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/1572391871.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+11%2C+2008&author=Christina+Pazzanese&pub=Boston+Globe&desc=Super+88+shifts+course+as+competition+mounts+Asian+market+chain+to+shut+3+stores%2C+renovate+others&pqatl=google|subscription=yes|title=Super 88 shifts course as competition mounts Asian market chain to shut 3 stores, renovate others|publisher=The Boston Globe|date=2008-10-11|accessdate=2011-06-26|page=A13|language=en|archive-date=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107070626/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/1572391871.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+11,+2008&author=Christina+Pazzanese&pub=Boston+Globe&desc=Super+88+shifts+course+as+competition+mounts+Asian+market+chain+to+shut+3+stores,+renovate+others&pqatl=google|dead-url=no}} "This year, H Mart, a national chain specializing in Asian foods, unveiled plans"</ref>集团经营Super韓亞龍超市。<ref name="Hispanic1">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/10/06/AR2007100601389.html|first=Cecilia|last=Kang|title=Koreans, Hispanics Work for Harmony|trans_title=韩裔及西班牙裔和谐共处|language=en|publisher=The Washington Post|date=2007-10-07|accessdate=2011-06-26|archive-date=2012-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112163921/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/10/06/AR2007100601389.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>“韓亞龍”（{{lang-ko|한아름}}）在[[韩语|韩语]]的意思是“一手满载商品”。<ref name="About">{{cite web|url=http://company.hmart.com/eng/company_history.asp|title=公司历史|publisher=H Mart|accessdate=2011-06-26|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111024204623/http://company.hmart.com/eng/company_history.asp|archivedate=2011-10-24}}</ref>

